            <fw type="dateline">1871</fw> <fw type="running">PARLIAMENTARY REPORTER.</fw> <fw type="num">321</fw>
            
            
            <p>
     <persName ref="pers:HOOP1">Mr. HOOPER</persName>.- I was elected to assist in 
     <lb/>maintaining and preserving our constitution,<lb/>and oppose Confederation. That is the<lb/>purpose for which I was elected. I am<lb/>not sure that Confederation is not at the<lb/>bottom of this very railroad scheme; I<lb/>am inclined to think it is.<lb/>
            </p>
